game.name: Subway Bunny Run Rush Rabbit Runner Game
game.description:
Are you a fan of a popular running challenge named Subway Surfers? If yes, then you must try out Subway Bunny Run Rush Rabbit Runner, which is not less than a treat for all the running game lovers. In this brand new adventure game, you have to control a cute and mischievous little rabbit that is on a mission on a mission of grabbing lots of carrots for this Easter. However, his path is full of dangerous obstacles that will try to stop him from moving forward.

Being a pro gamer you know how to handle the hindrances and keep your character running forward while avoiding the obstacles. Your character will keep running, but you have to control his direction. Make him right, left and slide through the obstacles at several instances while also collecting as much carrots as you can in this HTML5 platform game! Try not to touch your character with rocks, hurdles and any other obstacles otherwise you will lose your game!

Do not forget to collect the diamonds along the way to boost your score in this bradn new adventure game. This highly addictive and adventurous run game features simple controls, cool colorful graphics and seamless gameplay. You might take some time to keep up the pace of the game. However, you would try out this bunny running challenge again and again if you have played it for several minutes. Good luck to stay for as long as possible to create your best new score!
